%N A012475 a(n) = (2*n+1) [x^(2*n+1)] arctan(cos(x)*sin(x)).
%F A012475 A(0,k) = 1 and A(n,k) = -(k*(k+1) * A(n-1,k+2) + 4*k^2 * A(n-1,k)) for n > 0. a(n) = A(n,1). - _Seiichi Manyama_, Apr 16 2026
%e A012475 arctan(cos(x)*sin(x)) = x - 6/3!*x^3 + 120/5!*x^5 - 7056/7!*x^7 + 758400/9!*x^9 ...
%o A012475 (PARI) a(n, k=1) = if(n==0, 1, -(k*(k+1)*a(n-1, k+2)+4*k^2*a(n-1, k))); \\ _Seiichi Manyama_, Apr 16 2026
